Plot:

The beautiful, petite showgirl Arcadia Lake has a particular passion for playing nurse. Under this pretense, Arcadia visits and teases a stranger in the hospital bed until she finally gives him a show he won't soon forget. She leaves her silk stocking on her long, sexy legs so that the patient is stunned by her beauty. Eric Edwards, as the patient, opens Arcadia's world up to intensities of pain and pleasure of Greek-style of loving. Another of Arcadia's sexual passions is the loving, sensitive touch of a lesbian encounter. This Arcadia satisfies in a secret session with a warm and friendly Latin nurse and later at home with luscious Tina Blair. Arcadia lives out a final fantasy when she and her boyfriend, Eric, are taking home movies with Tina Blair and her lover. In the heat of passion with Eric. Arcadia is overwhelmed by a craving for Eric's special way of Greek love, and he gives it to her once again
